---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<main class="profile-screen" aria-labelledby="profile-title">
		<a class="back-link" href="/" aria-label="Volver al menu principal">Back</a>

		<header class="profile-header">
			<div class="screen-icon" aria-hidden="true">
				<img src="/img/menu/3.png" alt="" width="46" height="46" />
			</div>
			<h1 id="profile-title">Player Profile</h1>
		</header>

		<section class="profile-hero" aria-label="Player Profile intro">
			<div class="card-zone" aria-hidden="true">
				<img class="sprite sprite--bulbasaur" src="/img/profile/13.png" alt="" />
				<img class="sprite sprite--pokeball-top" src="/img/profile/10.png" alt="" />
				<img class="sprite sprite--cat" src="/img/profile/12.png" alt="" />
				<img class="sprite sprite--pokeball-bottom" src="/img/profile/11.png" alt="" />
				<img class="profile-card" src="/img/profile/lizbeth-card.png" alt="" />
			</div>

			<article class="intro-window">
				<img class="sprite sprite--charmander" src="/img/profile/14.png" alt="" aria-hidden="true" />
				<span class="window-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
				<div class="intro-copy">
					<p>
						Hi, I&apos;m Liz, a designer, developer, and naturally curious person from Mexico
						City who has always been drawn to creating things.
					</p>
					<p>
						Long before I understood what UX/UI or interactive design even meant, I was
						already fascinated by digital experiences through video games. I loved the
						feeling of exploring worlds, discovering interfaces, interacting with systems,
						and seeing how small details could completely shape an experience.
					</p>
					<p>
						Even as a kid, I knew I wanted to create something. I just didn&apos;t know what
						form that would take yet.
					</p>
				</div>
				<img class="sprite sprite--grass" src="/img/profile/9.png" alt="" aria-hidden="true" />
			</article>
		</section>

		<section class="ds-section" aria-label="Design journey">
			<article class="ds-text-window">
				<div class="ds-window-buttons" aria-hidden="true">
					<span></span>
					<span></span>
					<span></span>
				</div>
				<div class="ds-copy">
					<p>
						What eventually led me to design was realizing that creativity and technology
						never felt separate to me. I was naturally interested in both.
					</p>
					<p>
						I loved imagining ideas visually, but I was equally curious about how things
						actually worked underneath the surface. That&apos;s why interactive design felt so
						right: it allowed me to combine storytelling, systems, visuals, logic, and human
						behavior all in one place.
					</p>
					<p>
						Today, I work across UX/UI, frontend development, and interactive experiences,
						creating interfaces that aim to feel dynamic, intuitive, and accessible.
						Accessibility is especially important to me because I believe good design should
						work for everyone, not just look good.
					</p>
				</div>
			</article>

			<div class="ds-art" aria-hidden="true">
				<span class="sparkle sparkle--one"></span>
				<span class="sparkle sparkle--two"></span>
				<span class="sparkle sparkle--three"></span>
				<img class="ds-console" src="/img/profile/15.png" alt="" />
				<img class="ds-deco ds-deco--controller" src="/img/profile/16.png" alt="" />
				<img class="ds-deco ds-deco--tamagotchi" src="/img/profile/17.png" alt="" />
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="programming-background" class="programming-section" aria-label="Programming background">
			<div class="pikmin-stage">
				<div class="character-group">
					<div class="pikmin-row" aria-label="Pikmin-inspired pixel characters">
						<img src="/img/profile/18.png" alt="Red Pikmin-inspired pixel character" />
						<img src="/img/profile/19.png" alt="Gray Pikmin-inspired pixel character" />
						<img src="/img/profile/20.png" alt="Yellow Pikmin-inspired pixel character" />
						<img src="/img/profile/21.png" alt="Blue Pikmin-inspired pixel character" />
					</div>
					<img
						class="olimar-liz"
						src="/img/profile/olimar-liz.png"
						alt="Pixel-art Liz wearing an astronaut suit"
					/>
				</div>
			</div>

			<article class="code-window">
				<div class="code-window-bar" aria-hidden="true">
					<span></span>
					<span></span>
					<span></span>
				</div>
				<div class="code-window-body">
					<p>
						One thing that deeply shapes the way I design is my programming background. It
						allows me to move comfortably between both worlds: understanding user needs and
						creative direction while also understanding the technical side of how products
						are built. I genuinely enjoy being able to speak both languages and help bridge
						the gap between design and development.
					</p>
					<p>
						I love researching competitors, analyzing interfaces, building prototypes, and
						exploring how different products solve problems. For me, design is not only about
						aesthetics — it&apos;s about curiosity, experimentation, and creating experiences
						that feel alive.
					</p>
				</div>
			</article>
		</section>

		<section class="lore-section" aria-label="Personal lore">
			<article class="lore-window">
				<div class="lore-window-bar" aria-hidden="true">
					<span></span>
				</div>
				<div class="lore-window-body">
					<p>
						Outside of work, I spend a lot of time playing video games, listening to music,
						collecting pins and postcards, and constantly learning new things just because
						they spark my curiosity. I&apos;m the kind of person who gets excited about
						discovering a clever interaction, a beautifully crafted interface, or a creative
						concept executed thoughtfully.
					</p>
					<p>
						At the core of everything I create is the same thing that inspired me when I was
						younger: the idea that digital experiences can make people feel something.
					</p>
					<p>And honestly, that&apos;s still the part I love the most.</p>
				</div>
			</article>

			<div class="lore-art">
				<img
					src="/img/profile/princess-castle-scene.png"
					alt="Pixel-art princess beside a flag and pastel castle"
				/>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style is:global>
	@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Comfortaa:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Pixelify+Sans:wght@400..700&display=swap');

	body {
		overflow-x: hidden;
		background: #ffffec;
	}

	*,
	*::before,
	*::after {
		box-sizing: border-box;
	}

	.profile-screen {
		position: relative;
		min-height: 100svh;
		padding: clamp(92px, 12vh, 124px) clamp(24px, 7vw, 108px) 72px;
		background: #ffffec;
		color: #2b2b33;
		font-family: 'Comfortaa', 'Trebuchet MS', sans-serif;
	}

	.back-link {
		position: fixed;
		top: 24px;
		left: 24px;
		z-index: 5;
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		min-width: 92px;
		min-height: 34px;
		border-radius: 10px;
		background: #f3a4ba;
		color: #6b5260;
		font-size: 0.78rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	.profile-header {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 18px;
		width: min(100%, 1160px);
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding-left: clamp(44px, 5vw, 72px);
		color: #b8977a;
	}

	.screen-icon {
		display: grid;
		place-items: center;
		width: 82px;
		aspect-ratio: 1;
		border: 4px solid #d6c6f5;
		border-radius: 22px;
		background: #ffffff;
		box-shadow: 0 12px 26px rgba(214, 198, 245, 0.2);
	}

	.screen-icon img,
	.sprite {
		object-fit: contain;
		image-rendering: pixelated;
	}

	.profile-header h1 {
		margin: 0;
		font-family: 'Pixelify Sans', 'Courier New', monospace;
		font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 5vw, 4.35rem);
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0;
		line-height: 1;
	}

	.profile-hero {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: minmax(250px, 0.78fr) minmax(400px, 1.4fr);
		align-items: center;
		gap: clamp(24px, 5vw, 84px);
		width: min(100%, 1160px);
		margin: clamp(70px, 11vh, 112px) auto 0;
	}

	.card-zone {
		position: relative;
		min-height: 430px;
		overflow: visible;
	}

	.profile-card {
		position: absolute;
		left: 50%;
		top: 50%;
		width: min(305px, 31vw);
		max-width: 340px;
		filter: drop-shadow(0 14px 0 rgba(52, 52, 90, 0.12));
		transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(-11deg);
		transform-origin: center;
	}

	.intro-window {
		position: relative;
		min-height: 330px;
		padding: 42px 10px 10px;
		border-radius: 40px;
		background: #f5acd1;
	}

	.intro-copy {
		min-height: 100%;
		padding: 20px 34px 22px;
		background: #ffffff;
		border-radius: 0 0 30px 30px;
	}

	.intro-copy p {
		margin: 0 0 14px;
		color: #2b2b33;
		font-size: clamp(0.86rem, 1.1vw, 1rem);
		line-height: 2.2;
	}

	.intro-copy p:last-child {
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	.window-dot {
		position: absolute;
		top: 9px;
		right: 54px;
		width: 28px;
		height: 28px;
		border-radius: 999px;
		background: #a9f37c;
	}

	.sprite {
		position: absolute;
		z-index: 2;
		pointer-events: none;
	}

	.sprite--bulbasaur {
		top: 52px;
		left: -54px;
		width: 58px;
	}

	.sprite--pokeball-top {
		top: 8px;
		right: -42px;
		width: 64px;
		transform: rotate(14deg);
	}

	.sprite--cat {
		right: -58px;
		bottom: 80px;
		width: 66px;
	}

	.sprite--pokeball-bottom {
		left: -40px;
		bottom: 10px;
		width: 58px;
	}

	.sprite--charmander {
		top: -56px;
		left: 72px;
		width: 58px;
	}

	.sprite--grass {
		right: -18px;
		bottom: -38px;
		width: 104px;
	}

	.ds-section {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: minmax(420px, 1.05fr) minmax(360px, 0.95fr);
		align-items: center;
		gap: clamp(46px, 8vw, 104px);
		width: min(100%, 1160px);
		margin: clamp(90px, 16vh, 142px) auto 0;
		padding-bottom: 58px;
	}

	.ds-text-window {
		position: relative;
		padding: 60px 22px 18px;
		border-radius: 34px;
		background: #b8d9f8;
	}

	.ds-window-buttons {
		position: absolute;
		top: 20px;
		right: 28px;
		display: flex;
		gap: 24px;
	}

	.ds-window-buttons span {
		width: 28px;
		height: 28px;
		border-radius: 999px;
		background: #ffe28a;
	}

	.ds-window-buttons span:nth-child(2) {
		background: #8beb6f;
	}

	.ds-window-buttons span:nth-child(3) {
		background: #f7a4bf;
	}

	.ds-copy {
		padding: 20px 18px;
		border-radius: 0 0 28px 28px;
		background: #ffffff;
	}

	.ds-copy p {
		margin: 0 0 20px;
		color: #2b2b33;
		font-size: clamp(0.86rem, 1.05vw, 0.98rem);
		line-height: 2.35;
	}

	.ds-copy p:last-child {
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	.ds-art {
		position: relative;
		min-height: 460px;
	}

	.ds-console {
		position: absolute;
		top: 50%;
		left: 52%;
		width: min(420px, 38vw);
		transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
		image-rendering: pixelated;
	}

	.ds-deco {
		position: absolute;
		z-index: 2;
		object-fit: contain;
		image-rendering: pixelated;
		pointer-events: none;
	}

	.ds-deco--controller {
		left: 0;
		bottom: 18px;
		width: 118px;
		transform: rotate(10deg);
	}

	.ds-deco--tamagotchi {
		top: 8px;
		right: 0;
		width: 78px;
		transform: rotate(12deg);
	}

	.sparkle {
		position: absolute;
		width: 24px;
		height: 24px;
		border: 4px solid #a98ee9;
		transform: rotate(45deg);
	}

	.sparkle::before,
	.sparkle::after {
		position: absolute;
		content: '';
		background: #a98ee9;
	}

	.sparkle::before {
		top: 8px;
		left: -22px;
		width: 14px;
		height: 4px;
		box-shadow: 54px 0 0 #a98ee9;
	}

	.sparkle::after {
		top: -22px;
		left: 8px;
		width: 4px;
		height: 14px;
		box-shadow: 0 54px 0 #a98ee9;
	}

	.sparkle--one {
		top: 78px;
		left: 38px;
	}

	.sparkle--two {
		top: 38px;
		left: 86px;
		width: 18px;
		height: 18px;
	}

	.sparkle--three {
		right: 28px;
		bottom: 70px;
		width: 18px;
		height: 18px;
	}

	.programming-section {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: minmax(300px, 0.36fr) minmax(620px, 0.64fr);
		align-items: center;
		gap: clamp(76px, 9vw, 128px);
		width: min(100%, 1160px);
		margin: clamp(86px, 14vh, 130px) auto 0;
		padding: 34px 0 54px;
	}

	.pikmin-stage {
		display: flex;
		align-items: flex-end;
		justify-content: center;
		min-height: 300px;
		padding-left: 24px;
		overflow: visible;
	}

	.character-group {
		display: flex;
		align-items: flex-end;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 18px;
		overflow: visible;
	}

	.olimar-liz {
		width: auto;
		height: clamp(170px, 15vw, 220px);
		object-fit: contain;
		image-rendering: pixelated;
	}

	.pikmin-row {
		display: flex;
		align-items: flex-end;
		gap: 12px;
		padding-bottom: 0;
		overflow: visible;
	}

	.pikmin-row img {
		width: auto;
		height: clamp(60px, 5.2vw, 80px);
		object-fit: contain;
		image-rendering: pixelated;
	}

	.pikmin-row img:nth-child(2) {
		transform: none;
	}

	.pikmin-row img:nth-child(3) {
		transform: none;
	}

	.pikmin-row img:nth-child(4) {
		transform: none;
	}

	.code-window {
		width: min(760px, 100%);
		overflow: hidden;
		border: 10px solid #cdb4f5;
		border-radius: 28px;
		background: #ffffff;
		color: #4a403a;
		outline: 0;
		box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(214, 198, 245, 0.22);
		transition:
			transform 180ms ease,
			box-shadow 180ms ease;
	}

	.code-window:hover {
		box-shadow: 0 20px 42px rgba(214, 198, 245, 0.26);
		transform: translateY(-4px);
	}

	.code-window-bar {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: flex-end;
		gap: 16px;
		height: 40px;
		padding: 0 24px;
		background: #cdb4f5;
	}

	.code-window-bar span {
		width: 18px;
		height: 18px;
		border-radius: 999px;
		background: #f9e7a3;
	}

	.code-window-bar span:nth-child(2) {
		background: #b8f2a3;
	}

	.code-window-bar span:nth-child(3) {
		background: #f9c4d2;
	}

	.code-window-body {
		padding: 24px 32px;
		background: #ffffff;
	}

	.code-window-body p {
		margin: 0 0 18px;
		color: #4a403a;
		font-size: clamp(0.88rem, 1vw, 0.94rem);
		line-height: 1.8;
	}

	.code-window-body p:last-child {
		margin-bottom: 0;
		color: #6b625d;
	}

	.lore-section {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: minmax(460px, 0.54fr) minmax(360px, 0.46fr);
		align-items: center;
		gap: clamp(56px, 8vw, 112px);
		width: min(100%, 1160px);
		margin: clamp(86px, 14vh, 132px) auto 0;
		padding: 28px 0 70px;
	}

	.lore-window {
		overflow: hidden;
		border: 10px solid #a8d870;
		border-radius: 28px;
		background: #ffffff;
		box-shadow: 0 18px 34px rgba(168, 216, 112, 0.16);
	}

	.lore-window-bar {
		position: relative;
		height: 42px;
		background: #a8d870;
	}

	.lore-window-bar span {
		position: absolute;
		top: 50%;
		right: 26px;
		width: 20px;
		height: 20px;
		border-radius: 999px;
		background: #f9e7a3;
		transform: translateY(-50%);
	}

	.lore-window-body {
		padding: 30px 34px 34px;
		background: #f8f8f8;
	}

	.lore-window-body p {
		margin: 0 0 22px;
		color: #4a403a;
		font-size: clamp(0.96rem, 1.15vw, 1.06rem);
		line-height: 1.8;
	}

	.lore-window-body p:last-child {
		margin-bottom: 0;
		color: #6b625d;
	}

	.lore-art {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		min-height: 390px;
	}

	.lore-art img {
		width: min(500px, 43vw);
		max-width: 100%;
		object-fit: contain;
		image-rendering: pixelated;
	}

	@media (max-width: 980px) {
		.profile-screen {
			padding-inline: clamp(22px, 5vw, 42px);
		}

		.profile-header {
			padding-left: 0;
		}

		.profile-hero,
		.ds-section,
		.programming-section,
		.lore-section {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			width: 100%;
			max-width: 760px;
		}

		.profile-hero {
			margin-top: clamp(54px, 8vh, 72px);
		}

		.card-zone {
			min-height: 400px;
		}

		.profile-card {
			width: min(300px, 48vw);
		}

		.sprite--bulbasaur {
			left: 8%;
		}

		.sprite--pokeball-top {
			right: 12%;
		}

		.sprite--cat {
			right: 12%;
		}

		.sprite--pokeball-bottom {
			left: 10%;
		}

		.ds-section,
		.programming-section,
		.lore-section {
			gap: 42px;
			margin-top: 76px;
		}

		.ds-art {
			min-height: 380px;
			order: -1;
		}

		.ds-console {
			width: min(380px, 70vw);
		}

		.programming-section {
			padding-top: 10px;
		}

		.pikmin-stage {
			order: -1;
			padding-left: 0;
		}

		.code-window,
		.lore-window {
			width: 100%;
			max-width: 100%;
		}

		.lore-art {
			min-height: auto;
		}

		.lore-art img {
			width: min(440px, 82vw);
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 760px) {
		.profile-screen {
			padding: 96px 22px 64px;
		}

		.profile-header {
			padding-left: 0;
		}

		.screen-icon {
			width: 72px;
			border-radius: 20px;
		}

		.profile-hero {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			margin-top: 56px;
		}

		.card-zone {
			min-height: 390px;
		}

		.profile-card {
			left: 50%;
			width: min(290px, 72vw);
		}

		.sprite--bulbasaur {
			left: 12%;
		}

		.sprite--pokeball-top {
			right: 16%;
		}

		.sprite--cat {
			right: 18%;
		}

		.intro-window {
			min-height: auto;
		}

		.sprite--bulbasaur {
			left: 8%;
		}

		.sprite--pokeball-top {
			right: 10%;
		}

		.sprite--cat {
			right: 12%;
		}

		.sprite--pokeball-bottom {
			left: 12%;
		}

		.ds-section {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			margin-top: 72px;
		}

		.ds-text-window {
			padding: 56px 14px 14px;
			border-radius: 26px;
		}

		.ds-window-buttons {
			gap: 14px;
		}

		.ds-art {
			min-height: 360px;
			order: -1;
		}

		.ds-console {
			width: min(360px, 88vw);
		}

		.ds-deco--controller {
			left: 4%;
		}

		.ds-deco--tamagotchi {
			right: 8%;
		}

		.programming-section {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 32px;
			margin-top: 72px;
		}

		.pikmin-stage {
			min-height: 250px;
			order: -1;
			padding-left: 0;
		}

		.character-group {
			transform: none;
		}

		.olimar-liz {
			height: clamp(132px, 36vw, 170px);
		}

		.pikmin-row img {
			height: clamp(46px, 12vw, 62px);
		}

		.lore-section {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 38px;
			margin-top: 72px;
		}

		.lore-window {
			width: 100%;
		}

		.lore-art {
			min-height: auto;
		}

		.lore-art img {
			width: min(420px, 92vw);
		}
	}

